ipa District]]\n| \n|\n| Cambridge Road \u2013 [[Cambridge, New Zealand|Cambridge]] (west)\n| Northbound entrance and southbound exit\n|-\n| rowspan=3| Cambridge\n|\n|\n| {{jct|country=NZL|SH|1B|name1=Victoria Road}} \u2013 Cambridge, Hautapu\n|\n|-\n|\n|\n| Tirau Road (north)\u2013 Cambridge\n| Northbound exit and southbound entrance \n|-\n|\n|\n| {{jct|country=NZL|SH|1|name1=Tirau Road|dir1=south}} \u2013 [[Rotorua]], [[Taupo]]\n| ''Waikato Expressway ends''<br />{{coord|-37.8967|175.50796|format=dms|name=End of Waikato Expressway|type:landmark_region:NZ-WKO|display=inline}} \n|}\n\n===Mangaharakeke Drive (Te Rapa spur)===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! [[Territorial authority]] \n! Location\n! [[Exit number|Exit]]\n! Destination\n! Notes\n|- \n| rowspan=2| Waikato District\n| rowspan=2| Horsham Downs\n|\n| [[File:State Highway 1 NZ.svg|20px]] [[New Zealand State Highway 1|SH 1]] Waikato Expressway north <br> [[Huntly, New Zealand|Huntly]], [[Auckland]]\n| ''Mangaharakeke Drive begins'' <br> No east to south connection <br> \n|-style=\"background:#FFDEAD;\" \n|\n| Lake Road\n| Northbound exit only <br> to Waikato Expressway southbound (future)\n|- style=\n| rowspan=2| Waikato District\u2013Hamilton City boundary\n| Horotiu\n|\n| Great South Road/Te Rapa Road \u2013 [[Te Rapa]], Ngaruawahia\n|Crosses [[Waikato River]] on [[Horotiu#2013 Waikato Expressway bridge|Te Rehu O Waikato Bridge]]\n|- \n| Burbush\n|\n| {{jct|country=NZL|SH|39|name1=Koura Drive}} \u2013 [[Raglan, New Zealand|Raglan]], [[Otorohanga]]\n| \n|- \n| rowspan=2| [[Hamilton, New Zealand|Hamilton City]]\n| rowspan=2| Avalon\n| \n| Wairere Drive/Te Wetini Drive\n| Southbound exit and northbound entrance\n|- \n|\n| Avalon Drive\n| ''Mangaharakeke Drive ends''\n|}\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of motorways and expressways in New Zealand]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.nzta.govt.nz/projects/waikato-expressway/index.html Official website]\n*[http://www.fletcherconstruction.co.nz/news/2017/september-2017/biggest-roading-project-in-hamilton video of 10 min flyover of Hamilton bypass route in September 2017]\n\n{{New Zealand motorway list}}\n\n[[Category:Roads in New Zealand]]\n[[Category:Transport in Waikato]]\n[[Category:New Zealand State Highway 1]]\n", "name_user": "Onco p53", "label": "safe", "comment": "clean up, replaced: Ngaruawahia \u2192 Ng\u0101ruaw\u0101hia (6)  as perWikipedia:Naming_conventions_(New_Zealand)and https://gazetteer.linz.govt.nz/place/32480,typo(s) fixed: didn\u2019t \u2192 didn't", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Waikato_Expressway"}
{"title_page": "Golden Raspberry Award for Worst Actress", "text_new": "{{original research|date=February 2020}}\n{{Infobox award\n| image         =\n| image_upright = 0.7\n| caption       =\n| description    = Worst in film\n| presenter      = Golden Raspberry Award Foundation\n| country        = United States\n| year           = 1981{{cn|date=February 2020}}\n| holder         = [[Hilary Duff]], <br> ''[[The Haunting of Sharon Tate]]'' (2019)\n| website        = {{url|razzies.com}}\n}}\n'''Razzie Award for Worst Actress''' is an award presented at the annual [[Golden Raspberry Awards]] to the worst actress of the previous year. Male actors performing in [[Drag (clothing)|drag]] are eligible, as it is intended as a humorous award.\n\nThe following is a list of recipients and nominees of that award, along with the films for which they were nominated.\n\n==Winners and nominees==\n{{unreferenced section|date=February 2020}}\n===1980s===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:100%\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#bebebe\"\n! width=\"5%\" | Year\n! width=\"30%\" | Actress\n! width=\"35%\" | Film\n! width=\"30%\" | Character\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86;\"\n| rowspan=\"10\" |'''1980'''<br /><small>([[1st Golden Raspberry Awards|1st]])</small>\n|'''[[Brooke Shields]]'''\n|'''''[[The Blue Lagoon (1980 film)|The Blue Lagoon]]'''''\n|'''Emmeline Lestrange'''\n|-\n| [[Nancy Allen (actress)|Nancy Allen]]\n| ''[[Dressed to Kill (1980 film)|Dressed to Kill]]''\n| Liz Blake\n|-\n| [[Faye Dunaway]]\n| ''[[The First Deadly Sin]]''\n| Barbara Delaney\n|-\n| [[Shelley Duvall]]\n| ''[[The Shining (film)|The Shining]]''\n| Wendy Torrance\n|-\n| [[Farrah Fawcett]]\n| ''[[Saturn 3]]''\n| Alex\n|-\n| [[Sondra Locke]]\n| ''[[Bronco Billy]]''\n| Antoinette Lily\n|-\n| [[Olivia Newton-John]]\n| ''[[Xanadu (film)|Xanadu]]''\n| [[Terpsichore|Kira]]\n|-\n| [[Valerie Perrine]]\n| ''[[Can't Stop the Music]]''\n| Samantha Simpson\n|-\n| [[Deborah Raffin]]\n| ''[[Touched by Love]]''\n| Lena Canada\n|-\n| 