ary 2020}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:100%\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#bebebe\"\n! width=\"5%\" | Year\n! width=\"30%\" | Actress\n! width=\"35%\" | Film\n! width=\"30%\" | Character\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86;\"\n| rowspan=\"6\" |'''2000'''<br /><small>([[21st Golden Raspberry Awards|21st]])</small>\n|'''[[Madonna (entertainer)|Madonna]]'''\n|'''''[[The Next Best Thing]]'''''\n|'''Abbie Reynolds'''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Kim Basinger]]\n| ''[[Bless the Child]]''\n| Maggie O'Connor\n|-\n| ''[[I Dreamed of Africa]]''\n| [[Kuki Gallmann]]\n|-\n| [[Melanie Griffith]]\n| ''[[Cecil B. DeMented]]''\n| Honey Whitlock\n|-\n| [[Bette Midler]]\n| ''[[Isn't She Great]]''\n| [[Jacqueline Susann]]\n|-\n| [[Demi Moore]]\n| ''[[Passion of Mind]]''\n| Martha Marie / 'Marty' Talridge\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86;\"\n| rowspan=\"9\" |'''2001'''<br /><small>([[22nd Golden Raspberry Awards|22nd]])</small>\n|'''[[Mariah Carey]]'''\n|'''''[[Glitter (film)|Glitter]]'''''\n|'''Billie Frank'''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[Pen\u00e9lope Cruz]]\n| ''[[Blow (film)|Blow]]''\n| Mirtha Jung\n|-\n| ''[[Captain Corelli's Mandolin (film)|Captain Corelli's Mandolin]]''\n| Pelagia\n|-\n| ''[[Vanilla Sky]]''\n| Sofia Serrano\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Angelina Jolie]]\n| ''[[Lara Croft: Tomb Raider]]''\n| [[Lara Croft]]\n|-\n| ''[[Original Sin (2001 film)|Original Sin]]''\n| Julia Russell / Bonny Castle\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Jennifer Lopez]]\n| ''[[Angel Eyes (film)|Angel Eyes]]''\n| Sharon Pogue\n|-\n| ''[[The Wedding Planner]]''\n| Mary Fiore\n|-\n| [[Charlize Theron]]\n| ''[[Sweet November (2001 film)|Sweet November]]''\n| Sara Deever\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86;\"\n| rowspan=\"6\" |'''2002'''<br /><small>([[23rd Golden Raspberry Awards|23rd]])</small>\n|'''[[Madonna (entertainer)|Madonna]] (tie)'''\n|'''''[[Swept Away (2002 film)|Swept Away]]'''''\n|'''Amber Leighton'''\n|-\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86;\"\n| '''[[Britney Spears]] (tie)'''\n| '''''[[Crossroads (2002 film)|Crossroa