y Lohan]]\n{{col-end}}\n===Multiple nominations===\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-break}}\n'''6 nominations'''{{cn|date=February 2020}}\n*[[Melanie Griffith]]\n*[[Madonna (entertainer)|Madonna]]\n*[[Demi Moore]]\n   \n'''5 nominations{{cn|date=February 2020}}\n*[[Kim Basinger]]\n*[[Jennifer Lopez]]\n*[[Sharon Stone]]\n*[[Tyler Perry]] (in drag)\n   \n'''4 nominations'''{{cn|date=February 2020}}\n*[[Hilary Duff]] \n*[[Faye Dunaway]]\n*[[Angelina Jolie]]\n\n'''3 nominations'''{{cn|date=February 2020}}\n*[[Jessica Alba]]\n*[[Linda Blair]]\n*[[Bo Derek]]\n*[[Cameron Diaz]]\n*[[Megan Fox]]\n*[[Katherine Heigl]]\n*[[Lindsay Lohan]]\n*[[Brigitte Nielsen]]\n*[[Sarah Jessica Parker]]\n*[[Brooke Shields]]\n*[[Kristen Stewart]]\n*[[Sean Young]]\n{{col-break}}\n\n'''2 nominations'''{{cn|date=February 2020}}\n*[[Drew Barrymore]]\n*[[Halle Berry]]\n*[[Sandra Bullock]]\n*[[Joan Chen]]\n*[[Miley Cyrus]]\n*[[Whoopi Goldberg]]\n*[[Anne Hathaway]]\n*[[Dakota Johnson]]\n*[[Milla Jovovich]]\n*[[Sondra Locke]]\n*[[Melissa McCarthy]]\n*[[Bette Midler]]\n*[[Olivia Newton-John]]\n*[[Julia Roberts]]\n*[[Tanya Roberts]]\n*[[Ally Sheedy]]\n*[[Talia Shire]]\n*[[Barbra Streisand]]\n*[[Charlize Theron]]\n*[[Uma Thurman]]\n*[[Naomi Watts]]\n*[[Pia Zadora]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n<!--Do not need to place razzies.com as external link; website appears in the infobox.-->\n*[https://www.imdb.com/event/ev0000558/overview/?ref_=ev_sa_1 Golden Raspberry Awards] at the [[Internet Movie Database]]\n{{Golden Raspberry Award Years}}\n{{Portal|Film}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Golden Raspberry Award For Worst Actress}}\n[[Category:Golden Raspberry Awards by category|Actress]]\n[[Category:Film awards for lead actress]]\n", "text_old": "{{multiple issues|\n{{original research|date=February 2020}}\n{{unreferenced|date=February 2020}}\n}}\n{{Infobox award\n| image         =\n| image_upright = 0.7\n| caption       =\n| description    = Worst in film\n| presenter      = Golden Raspberry Award Foundation\n| country        = United States\n| year           = 1981{{cn|date=February 2020}}\n| holder         = [[Hilary Duff]], <br> ''[[The Haunting of Sharon Tate]]'' (2019)\n| website        = {{url|razzies.com}}\n}}\n'''Razzie Award for Worst Actress''' is an award presented at the annual [[Golden Raspberry Awards]] to the worst actress of the previous year. Male actors performing in [[Drag (clothing)|drag]] are eligible, as it is intended as a humorous award.\n\nThe following is a list of recipients and nominees of that award, along with the films for which they were nominated.\n\n==Winners and nominees==\n{{unreferenced section|date=February 2020}}\n===1980s===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:100%\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#bebebe\"\n! width=\"5%\" | Year\n! width=\"30%\" | Actress\n! width=\"35%\" | Film\n! width=\"30%\" | Character\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86;\"\n| rowspan=\"10\" |'''1980'''<br /><small>([[1st Golden Raspberry Awards|1st]])</small>\n|'''[[Brooke Shields]]'''\n|'''''[[The Blue Lagoon (1980 film)|The Blue Lagoon]]'''''\n|'''Emmeline Lestrange'''\n|-\n| [[Nancy Allen (actress)|Nancy Allen]]\n| ''[[Dressed to Kill (1980 film)|Dressed to Kill]]''\n| Liz Blake\n|-\n| [[Faye Dunaway]]\n| ''[[The First Deadly Sin]]''\n| Barbara Delaney\n|-\n| [[Shelley Duvall]]\n| ''[[The Shining (film)|The Shining]]''\n| Wendy Torrance\n|-\n| [[Farrah Fawcett]]\n| ''[[Saturn 3]]''\n| Alex\n|-\n| [[Sondra Locke]]\n| ''[[Bronco Billy]]''\n| Antoinette Lily\n|-\n| [[Olivia Newton-John]]\n| ''[[Xanadu (film)|Xanadu]]''\n| [[Terpsichore|Kira]]\n|-\n| [[Valerie Perrine]]\n| ''[[Can't Stop the Music]]''\n| Samantha Simpson\n|-\n| [[Deborah Raffin]]\n| ''[[Touched by Love]]''\n| Lena Canada\n|-\n| [[Talia Shire]]\n| ''[[Windows (film)|Windows]]''\n| Emily Hollander\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86;\"\n| rowspan=\"5\" |'''1981'''<br /><small>([[2nd Golden Raspberry Awards|2nd]])</small>\n|'''[[Bo Derek]] (tie)'''\n|'''''[[Tarzan, the Ape Man (1981 film)|Tarzan, 