 Young]]'''\n|'''''[[A Kiss Before Dying (1991 film)|A Kiss Before Dying]]'''''\n|'''Ellen Carlsson'''\n|-\n| [[Kim Basinger]]\n| ''[[The Marrying Man]]''\n| Vicki Anderson\n|-\n| [[Sally Field]]\n| ''[[Not Without My Daughter (film)|Not Without My Daughter]]''\n| [[Betty Mahmoody]]\n|-\n| [[Madonna (entertainer)|Madonna]]\n| ''[[Madonna: Truth or Dare|Truth or Dare]]''\n| Herself\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Demi Moore]]\n| ''[[The Butcher's Wife]]''\n| Marina Lemke\n|-\n| ''[[Nothing but Trouble (1991 film)|Nothing but Trouble]]''\n| Diane Lightson\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86;\"\n| rowspan=\"8\" |'''1992'''<br /><small>([[13th Golden Raspberry Awards|13th]])</small>\n| rowspan=\"2\" |'''[[Melanie Griffith]]'''\n|'''''[[Shining Through]]'''''\n|'''Linda Voss'''\n|-\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86;\"\n| '''''[[A Stranger Among Us]]'''''\n| '''Emily Eden'''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Kim Basinger]]\n| ''[[Cool World]]''\n| Holli Would\n|-\n| ''[[Final Analysis]]''\n| Heather Evans\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Lorraine Bracco]]\n| ''[[Medicine Man (film)|Medicine Man]]''\n| Dr. Rae Crane\n|-\n| ''[[Traces of Red]]''\n| Ellen Schofield\n|-\n| [[Whitney Houston]]\n| ''[[The Bodyguard (1992 film)|The Bodyguard]]''\n| Rachel Marron\n|-\n| [[Sean Young]]\n| ''[[Love Crimes (1992 film)|Love Crimes]]''\n| Dana Greenway\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86;\"\n| rowspan=\"5\" |'''1993'''<br /><small>([[14th Golden Raspberry Awards|14th]])</small>\n|'''[[Madonna (entertainer)|Madonna]]'''\n|'''''[[Body of Evidence (1993 film)|Body of Evidence]]'''''\n|'''Rebecca Carlson'''\n|-\n| [[Melanie Griffith]]\n| ''[[Born Yesterday (1993 film)|Born Yesterday]]''\n| Billie Dawn\n|-\n| [[Janet Jackson]]\n| ''[[Poetic Justice (film)|Poetic Justice]]''\n| Justice\n|-\n| [[Demi Moore]]\n| ''[[Indecent Proposal]]''\n| Diana Murphy\n|-\n| [[Sharon Stone]]\n| ''[[Sliver (film)|Sliver]]''\n| Carly Norris\n|- style=\"background:#FAEB86;\"\n| rowspan=\"6\" |'''1994'''<br /><small>([[15th Golden Raspberry Awards